message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product which has been carefully crafted to provide exceptional value. It comes with a variety of features designed to meet your needs. Considering its quality and benefits, I would like to propose a price of $120 for this item. I believe it offers great value and hope you'll find it worthwhile. Let me know what you think!
Thank you for your offer, Alice. I appreciate the value you're providing with your product. I would like to make a counteroffer of $100 for the product.
